description:
Witch's spellbook. It contains lots of various extraordinary spells 
that can help you change the world for good.
name: Spellbook

description:
The enigmatic ske... Lordy's Key that can unlock any door
in the game. Do not abuse it.
name: Lordy's key

description:
This beautiful flower for centuries suffered from playful maidens fingers
mercilessly tearing away petals. "Love - don’t love, chuck or hug".
name: Camomile

description:
You can hardly recognize that those torn rags are a dress. 
(useless trash)
name: Rags

description:
Dice made by Inzhir so it would give him luck in love affairs. That's
why he preffers not to use it for playing.
name: Inzhir's Dice

description:
Forbidden by the Church voulgar trash book by Eromur Abel a misterious
author who was never seen in public.
name: In the armory with Babett, p. 1

description:
A wonderful cedar cone. If used correctly it can make a real miracle...
though a small one. Your luck is increased by one point.
name: Cedar cone

description:
Mighty, long, tasty and quite a head. You can safely eat this noble
mushroom raw (not grub-ridden).
name: Porcini

description:
A cucumber from Fartthew's pants. So big and thick and papulose. It 
seems it was grown to satisfy quite a different kind of hunger.
name: Huge cucumber

description:
Forbidden by the Church voulgar trash book by Eromur Abel a misterious
author who was never seen in public.
name: Honey-bun from Zalesje, p. 3

description:
Not a nut for a gentle girl fingers. No, only a true master can deal with
a walnut. Your endurance is increased by one point.
name: Walnut

description:
Proud representative of an extremely rare golden royal bugs species. It is 
believed that if it bites your butt, it will bring you luck.
name: Golden royal bug

description:
It looks like a female's breast, it is juicy as a breast, it is elastic, 
as a breast. Perhaps it might be one?!
name: Melon

description:
Piece of torn letter found in Zalesje. It says about some materials, deal 
and a person named Vseslav. Signed by some Kras-Gor.
name: Part of a letter

description:
Piece of torn letter found in Zalesje. It says about some materials, deal
and a person named Vseslav.
name: Torn part of a letter

description:
Five juggling balls, gift from Rikka. You can always play them, when your 
hands are free. Practice never hurts.
name: Juggling balls

description:
Detailed map of the village, made in today's popular format - top view.
Old folks will scold, but young people like it.
name: Map of Zalesje

description:
Small loop towel. You can use it to dry face or hands or bottom...
lots of things. A towel always comes in handy.
name: Owned towel

description:
Tasty and healthy nut that strengthens health and gives self-confidence. 
Your strikingness is increased by one point.
name: Hazelnut

description:
Perfumed letter of your secret admirer. Nice paper, good handwriting and
a neat seal with heart on it. Someone put all his love into it.
name: Admirer's letter 11/08

description:
In the past, women used to put men to sleep with valerian, drag them to 
secluded places, and do some dirty things. Now this savagery is put away.
name: Pouch of allheal

description:
Small towel. You can use it to dry face or hands or bottom...
lots of things. A towel always comes in handy.
name: Towel

description:
Perfumed letter of your secret admirer. Nice paper, good handwriting and
a neat seal with heart on it. Someone put all his love into it.
name: Admirer's letter 09/05

description:
Perfumed letter of your secret admirer. Nice paper, good handwriting and
a neat seal with heart on it. Someone put all his love into it.
name: Admirer's letter 23/07

description:
Perfumed letter of your secret admirer. Nice paper, good handwriting and
a neat seal with heart on it. Someone put all his love into it.
name: Admirer's letter 03/01

description: Default Key, as default as possible.
name: Default Key

description: You hope to sell them?! That's a laugh!
name: Pile of leaves

description: Light beer that smells not only of hops, but also of orange and junipers.
name: Beer

description: A wood detail, which is part of some instrument.
name: Detail

description:
Wrinkled something, almost flat and unpleasant to the touch. Even on
such kind of good is in demand.
name: Elven melon

description:
It is said that while melons warm your hand, apples warm your heart. 
Applemelon is grown specifically to warm both the hand and the heart.
name: Applemelon

description:
A pale, delicate and highly succulent sort of melon. Although they 
don't have a milky taste, they are always luscious.
name: Lactic melon

description:
An ordinary melon, albeit with a little hue of pink. Resembles that of
a female's breast. Perhaps it might be one?!
name: Pink melon

description:
The biggest sort of melon grown in the kingdom. It's named after one 
girl. A damn fine girl she was.
name: "Alyonka" Melon

description:
It looks like a female's breast, it is juicy as a breast, it is elastic, 
as a breast. Perhaps it might be one?!
name: Melon

description:
A highly unstable, needy and hardy sort of melon. You'll have to endure 
some acidity to get a taste of it's tender sweetness.
name: Striped melon

description:
A tiny option for those who like small ones. It's a great way to get a 
little fun before you fall asleep.
name: Tickler

description:
A device of a really large size, and in combination with the black color
and the veins along the trunk... Anyway, it looks formidable.
name: Thug

description:
An incredibly long and thick sample. So big and heavy that you can kill
with it. Most likely designed as a joke.
name: Violet Delight

description:
The cheapest booze made from honey. It will sweeten your bitter life 
(it won't actually).
name: Medovukha

description:
It tastes like piss, and the color is not better, but still there are 
lovers.
name: Light beer

description: A long rainbow feather with a soft down part.
name: Feather of an unknown bird

description: An uncomplicated mahogany tool. Average size. Varnished.
name: Dildo

description: An uncomplicated mahogany tool, carefully wrapped in cloth.
name: Dildo in the parcel

description:
This key craves to get into a narrow keyhole. Help it... 
and make it deeper.
name: Key to the room 7, "Spring"

description: An empty flower pot that has a pleasant smell of black soil.
name: Pot

description:
A pot with the very flowers that Rodinka likes so much.
"They’re wonderful", she would say.
name: Flower in a pot

description:
Before you drink from a vessel, you need to fill it. This, by the way, 
means that you can benefit even from an empty bottle.
name: Empty bottle

description:
There is no way to read the letter because of the wax seal. You wish 
you could do it.
name: The chief’s letter

description: It's not wine at all, it's booze. Red and sour hooch.
name: The cheapest wine

description:
A bottle of expensive currant wine with good aging. There is no chance 
of seducing the daughters of merchants without it.
name: "Scarlet Currant"

description:
Just like water, but only bitter and dark. It will please any 
beer lover.
name: Dark beer

description:
Juicy pie, tightly stuffed with hot porcini mushroom. Pleasure for both 
men and women.
name: Pie with mushrooms

description:
A small garden tool, indispensable for tidy work. It's unlikely you'll
see one of these by an ordinary person.
name: Shovel

description:
A marigold flower is like a little fire. It makes good medicine and 
a nice decoration.
name: Calendula

description:
No, this book will not tell you about a building's heat balance disorder
due to soot accumulation on the chimney walls.
name: About the pros of chimney sweeping

description:
The long-desired key. The key to the house. The key to a dream. The key 
to the future. Rusty, scratched, and bent.
name: The key to Dran's house

description:
Cute name and cute look. But this little buddy won't just bring you to 
your knees. No, it will squeeze all the juice out of you.
name: Honey bunny

description:
A bright-orange liquid splashes around in the bottle. The elixir might
combat the heat, but its very appearance warms you.
name: Dran's elixir

description: The incredible mixture, capable of sobering anyone up. Oh, if only it were.
name: Mug of sobering drink

description:
One part of a series of books about a good-hearted witch who wanders the
world and helps people with her magic. Church doesn't approve of it.
name: Witch and soldiers

description:
This oil moisturizes the skin and makes it easier to glide during 
intercourse. It can also be used against draconids.
name: Draconid oil

description:
The legendary sword used to chop off the heads of traitors to the 
kingdom and unfaithful wives (no dragons were killed with it).
name: "Death of Dragons"

description:
The alchemical ingredient brewed specifically to fight fire-breathing
wyverns.
name: Frost Salts

description: The cherished key for any adventurer.
name: Treasury key

description: The old sword of a long-dead hero.
name: Rusty sword

description:
This bottle is begging to be filled. That's its purpose, that's its
destiny.
name: Empty bottle

description:
The clean white handkerchief. Girls from noble families in the capital 
often use such handkerchiefs to blow their nose.
name: White handkerchief

description:
Deadly danger of the leaves and berries on this branch, only add to its
beauty.
name: Branch of belladonna

description:
It's the perfect porcini mushroom that a girl can only find once in her
life. Just kidding. There's a forest full of mushrooms like this.
name: Suitable porcini

description:
If that bottle hadn't been filled with animal urine, it would still feel
an oppressive emptiness inside.
name: Bottle with urine

description:
Physical evidence of someone's egregious crime. Only God knows whose blood
is on this handkerchief.
name: Bloody handkerchief

description:
This golden сhalice is old and decorated with various symbols. There is 
always water splashing in it, no matter how much you drink or pour it out.
name: Fire Chalice

description:
The clear liquid splashes in this bottle as if it wants to break the glass
and escape to freedom.
name: Bottle of water

description:
A strong brew from the Dorth tavern called "From ailments". In spite of its
name, it does not cure diseases, but only multiplies them.
name: Brew "From ailments"

description:
An elegantly written letter, on expensive paper, in a purple envelope, 
and scented with chrysanthemum.
name: Letter from the Countess

description: A gift from the Countess, wrapped in a snappy purple cloth.
name: Gift in a bundle

description:
A great tool if you want to enjoy the smell of wood and the sight of a 
whole bunch of lovely little shavings.
name: Hand Plane

description:
A true symbol of creation, hard work, steadfastness, firmness and 
masculinity. A simple and indispensable tool for any household.
name: Hammer

description: A great tool for pushing, kneading, self-satisfaction.
name: Witch's "Pestle"
